A romp through key years of Never Mind The Buzzcocks' 17-year run, combining the most engaging music news stories with a raft of Buzzcocks' memorable moments.

1/8 A look back at the year Never Mind the Buzzcocks was first shown and Take That split up.

2/8 The memorable moments in this edition include the split-up of Westlife in 2004

3/8 The memorable moments in this edition include Geri leaving the Spice Girls in 1998.

4/8 Featured memorable moments from 2006 include Simon Amstell making his Buzzcocks debut.

5/8 Memorable moments from 2001 include the break-up of Steps and the launch of Popstars.

6/8 A look back at 2007, the year Dappy and Preston made memorable appearances on the show.

7/8 A look back at 2000, the year Liam and Robbie fell out at the Brits.

8/8 A look back at 2008, including a moving tribute to Blue.
